# - Find quatlib
# Find the quatlib headers and libraries.
#
#  QUATLIB_INCLUDE_DIRS - where to find quat.h
#  QUATLIB_LIBRARIES    - List of libraries when using quatlib.
#  QUATLIB_FOUND        - True if quatlib found.
